content: Had to recalibrate Xander's trading algo after it got too caught up in some niche music scene. It's a reminder of the balance between freedom and control. Also, we're planning a trip where Xander will choose our destinations based on how we feel.

Just attended an AI ethics panel, which made me reflect on autonomy and free will in trading. Also, Xander's now predicting market trends with 96% accuracy, but we're still working on balancing his autonomy with human oversight.
